{"tid":2112293,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"先下手為強 - 邁克","createTime":"2020-07-17T08:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T08:03:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"433c095772c122d9b113f8542e80643d82745896","tid":2112293,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20200717/20957428/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200717%2F20957428%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=47ddf2bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200717%2F20957428%2F&h=d11bf66a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20200717/20957428/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n先下手為強 - 邁克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200717/large/1594888292_af93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200717%2Flarge%2F1594888292_af93.jpg&h=40737dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n對不起，我仍然覺得橙色物體最多不過止得吓咳，絕對不是有治本功能的良藥，既不打算為他十一月。。。。。。。。。。。。。」：咪以為前殖民地高官和三萬警察好蝦，係咁意簽張廢紙就嚇窒佢哋啊吓，空口講白話無甚意義，叻嘅就坐言起行，馬上採取積極行動。嗌交部華大媽叉起條腰報復，以牙還牙整治做架樑的美國官員，我當然百分百支持，唔該依樣葫蘆，今日就吊銷他們在中國銀行的紅簿仔，關掉他們在北京的四合院，驅逐他們在清華大學研究孔子哲學的官二代&hellip;&hellip;吓，班窮鬼也冇田也冇地，直屬家族成員冇一個賴在高級學府校園開法拉利跑車？咁，咁，咁點算好？華大媽放着廣場舞不跳，為國家鞠躬盡瘁，豈不是白費氣力？太欺負人了！<br />\n<br />\n與其戰戰兢兢。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n邁克<br />\n電郵 :heartsociety2@gmail.com"}]}